fr.enseeiht.danck.voice_analyzer

Interface Parser


  • public interface Parser
    A parser able to parse series of (Meta)Token and generating (Meta)Orders. Can be asked the next accepted Token for parsing.
    Author:
    Anaël Megna, Kilian Boulhaïs, Cyrius Nugier

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods

      Returns the set of Token accepted in the current state of the parsing process.

      • parse

        MetaOrder parse(MetaToken metaToken)
         throws UnknownOrderException
        Update the parser state according to the input (Meta)Token. If something has been understood, then returns the corresponding (Meta)Order.
        Parameters:
        metaToken - the MetaToken containing the Token to be parsed
        Returns:
        the MetaOrder containing the Order corresponding to the sequence of Token, or null if waiting for more Tokens
        Throws:
        UnknownOrderException - if no Order corresponds to the parsed Token sequence
